# Overview

This analysis comes from ["Eviction Notices" on DataSF.](https://data.sfgov.org/Housing-and-Buildings/Eviction-Notices/5cei-gny5/about_data) It was last exported at `r evictions_change`.

# Analysis

We built the following model:

`r extract_eq(model$model)`

```{r}
tbl_regression(model$model, intercept = TRUE)
```
